snippet.title: Best VGM 1353 - Vampire The Masquerade : Bloodlines - Chinatown
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1580 - http://youtu.be/bss8vzkIB74
Best VGM 2077 - https://youtu.be/Mn3HPClpZ6Q

Unofficial Patch here: http://www.patches-scrolls.com/vampire_bloodlines.php

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC
Vampire the Masquerade : Bloodlines (2004)
Chinatown
Rik Schaffer
